history.content: I'm really sorry this is frustrating.  Unfortunately, unless we teach classes 24 hours a day we are not going to be able to avoid all conflicts, especially between upper division and lower division classes.  We offer too many classes for this to be possible.  Of course, you can take 16A and could this semester but you made other choices this semester -- which is fine -- but the consequence is that your choices are more constrained this semester.

Is there any plan to remove the conflict between EE16A & CS 168? (that's what the new schedule planner says at least). This is the 3rd semester I haven't been able to get in or will get in but can't take 16A due to conflicts... this semester it was 170 and last semester I couldn't get into the class at all. This is extremely frustrating...
history.subject: Conflict between CS 168 & EE 16a?
